# IOM website — deploy & git safety

Repo: `F:\iom_website` → production **https://iobjectm.com** (Vercel, `master`).

## Deploy protocol

1. **Commit before deploy** — never run `npx vercel --prod` with uncommitted tracked changes.
2. **Push before deploy** — `git push origin master` so git matches production.
3. **Use** `npm run deploy:prod` (runs `pre-deploy-check.mjs`, build, push, Vercel).
4. Read **DEPLOY.md** for the full checklist and post-deploy verification.

## Git — never without user approval

- Do **not** run `git stash -u`, `git stash push -u`, or `git reset --hard`.
- Do **not** drop stash unless the user asked and stash was inspected vs HEAD.
- Prefer commit + push over deploy-only from a dirty tree.

## High-conflict files

Touch with care; always commit after edits:

- `src/data/projects.ts` — cards/sections (Web Export Kit, CRM Demo, demos)
- `src/utils/createMusicPlayerVisualizer.ts` / `musicPlayerFftOceanVisualizer.ts` — music animation
- `public/demos/**/index.html` — standalone demos (ssr-denoise, volume-lighting, etc.)
- `src/crm/**` — CRM demo + client login UI

